<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
   The shock waves ran from Syria to Switzerland after U.S. Navy
planes shot down two Libyan jet fighters over the Mediterranean,
with only Israel's top leadership cheering the U.S. fliers' feat.
   U.S. allies in Europe for the most part reserved comment after
Wednesday's action, although some expressed ``great concern'' and
